{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Messages were smuggled back and forth, and all that, even some of the pictures that were taken by this guy, [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Shmuelevitz ?], of the crematoria down there at one time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was a date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It is in publications, there you see women running on a field down there toward the crematorium naked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's one that was taken by [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Shmuelevitz ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was also a communist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But never mind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in any case, he amassed a fortune in gold bars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he met, [SIGHS] uh, an SS man down there that spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS man was raised by a Jewish family somewhere in Romania, and he was-- the SS man-- was an Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, he, uh-- how do you translate that thing, Volksdeutsche?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a German living in another country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a German by-- his great grandfather was a German, OK, so his blood was German, and this was how they took him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, he became an SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said he's going to give him, I don't know, 20 bars of gold, and da, da, da.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the guy said, yes, and he's gonna hide him in a-- in a-- in a-- in a cart with two horses down there, and he's going to be hidden in the straw, and da, da, da, and da, da.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he brought him back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He took the gold, and brought him back, and he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the significant thing is not what he did, because I don't think that he was a hero.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what he did was significant, especially to all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here's a guy that's an atheist.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
